name: .FXML File Extension
summary: Learn about .FXML files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Contains code written in the FXML programming language developed by Oracle Corporation; used to create the user interface of a JavaFX 2.0 application; based on XML which uses the .XML file extension.

content: JavaFX is used to develop rich internet applications and can use FXML to develop its user interfaces as opposed to writing it using procedural code. The FXML files is used alongside .JAVA files to create an application.
